# ── Secrets ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .env contains real API keys, JWT secrets, and the MASTER_KEY used to encrypt
# user API credentials at rest. NEVER commit it. (.env.example is fine — it's
# only placeholder values for documentation.)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ── Local SQLite artefacts (pre-Postgres migration) ─────────────────────────
# Production runs on Postgres (Neon), but legacy local SQLite files may still
# exist on dev machines from before the switch. Don't accidentally commit
# personal dev data.
*.db
*.db-journal
prisma/prisma/